node.text:
Busy loving & appreciating my pregnant body🤍🙏 I have currently gained almost 20lbs & lost a lot of muscle because I haven’t been lifting like before. I always thought I would be this super fit mom working out all the time during pregnancy but that has not been the case & I’m totally ok with it. Pregnancy looks different for everyone. Listen to your body and don’t let anyone push anything on to you. You know your body best! 

I’ve always been so big on how my body looks, but these last few months I’ve taken so many steps back and have just been focusing on how I feel! I know I’ll get back to my heavy training in no time, but for now my active days consist of resistance band work, walks, yoga, & meditation. Happy, healthy, growing & glowing 😬 #31WeeksPregnant

P.S. Willy in the back being a dog daddy & hyping me up like always😂
